            Figure figure,
            java.lang.String position,
            int status)
        Constructor 1, which creates a tile with a figure from its color, type of figure, position and status.
        Parameters:
        color - The background color of the tile.
        figure - The figure which its into the tile.
        position - The position of the tile into the mosaic.
        status - The status of the tile: 1 (Tile off), 2 (Tile on), 3 (Tile with figure in black).
